<ul>
  <li>show currently-active connections as well as their status ( ESTABLISH, LISTENING, TIME_WAITâ€¦) <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">netstat | grep LISTEN</code> check if server is listening</li>
  <li>network interface statistics</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">netstat -r</code> for routing table</li>
